shells.custom_fn:
if GameTime - Skill.og_start < 6.0 and hk.check_hotkey("Use Skill ".. Skill.idx, true) then
    Hold()
    RepeatNode()
else
    local ground_pts = Player["<CharaController>k__BackingField"]:get_NumGroundContactPoints()
    Player["<ActionManager>k__BackingField"]:requestActionCore(0, ground_pts == 0 and "JobMagicUser_EndLevitate" or "NormalLocomotion", 0)
    Kill()
end

if not Node.set_invis and Summon and GameTime - Node.start > 0.25 then
    Node.set_invis = true
    Summon:get_GameObject():set_DrawSelf(false)
    func.getC(Summon:get_GameObject(), "app.WwiseContainerApp"):call(".ctor()")
end

shells.custom_fn:
local corpse_ctrl = Node.em_soft_lock_enemy and Node.em_soft_lock_enemy._Chara:get_CorpseCtrl()
if not Node.em_soft_lock_enemy or (corpse_ctrl and corpse_ctrl:get_CorpseStep() >= 3) then
    Player:get_StaminaManager():set_RemainingAmount(Player:get_StaminaManager():get_RemainingAmount() + Skill.spell.stam_cost)
    Kill()
end

    Hold()

spells.activate_fn:
g_climb_summon = nil
for chr, nstore in pairs(sm_summons) do 
    if nstore and nstore.player_climbing then
        g_climb_summon = nstore
        return true
    end
end
return true

shells.custom_fn:
Stop()
if g_climb_summon then 
    local cam_matrix =  sdk.get_primary_camera():get_WorldMatrix()
    local end_pos = cam_matrix[3] + cam_matrix[2] * -300
    local gresults = func.cast_ray(cam_matrix[3], end_pos, 2, 0, 0, 0)[1]
    local coords = gresults and gresults[2] or end_pos
    g_climb_summon.command_summon_fn(coords)
    g_climb_summon = nil
else
    for chr, nstore in pairs(sm_summons) do
        if nstore then nstore.command_summon_fn(Node.ray[2]) end
    end
end
